<Layout title="Nicholas Charriere">
  <h1 class="text-4xl mb-6 font-bold text-heading">Hi, I'm Nick 👋</h1>
  <p>
    I'm an engineer and founder who loves building products. I care a lot about
    craft and I'm optimistic about technology and what it can do for the world.
    Currently building{" "}
    <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="https://getmocha.com">Mocha</a>{" "}with{" "}
    <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="https://benreinhart.com">Ben Reinhart</a>.
  </p>
  <p class="pt-6">
    Before that, I was a founding engineer at{" "}
    <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="https://privy.io">Privy</a>. I spent 4 years on the ML platform team at{" "}
    <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="https://getcruise.com">Cruise</a>, 2 years at{" "}
    <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="https://pinterest.com">Pinterest</a>{" "}
    building real-time ML systems, and a few years working full-stack at early-stage
    startups.
  </p>
  <p class="pt-6">
    I live in California but grew up in France (bonjour 🇫🇷), where I got my
    engineering Masters from{" "}
    <a
      class="text-link hover:underline"
      href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mines_Paris_%E2%80%93_PSL"
