  </p>
  <p class="pt-6">
    Find me on{" "}
    <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="https://x.com/nichochar">X</a>,{" "}
    <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="https://github.com/nichochar">GitHub</a>, and{" "}
    <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicholas-charriere/">LinkedIn</a>.
  </p>
</Layout>
